  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The witch can cause fate to twist so that it benefits a creature within 30 feet for 1 round. Whenever that creature is targeted by an effect that requires an attack roll, including weapon attacks, the attacker must roll twice and take the worse result.</p>\n<p>At 8th level and 16th level, the duration of this hex is extended by 1 round.</p>\n<p>A witch cannot use this ability on herself.</p>\n<p>Hexes that affect the fortune hex, such as cackle, also affect protective luck.</p>"
